Event.name: loadexception
Event.comment: Fires if an exception occurs in the Proxy during data loading. Note that this event is also relayed through {

Param.name: arg
Param.comment: The callback's arg object passed to the {@link #load} function

Param.name: null
Param.comment: This parameter does not apply and will always be null for MemoryProxy

Param.name: e
Param.comment: The JavaScript Error object caught if the configured Reader could not read the data
